PN,43101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781277116
OL,3,CEmergency ban on large boats fishing
OL,4,Cfor octopus close to the Cornish coast
OL,6,FCornwall's fishing industry is set to
OL,7,Fface new restrictions on octopus
OL,8,Ffishing after an emergency bylaw was
OL,9,Fvoted through at the county hall in
OL,10,FTruro.
OL,12,FThe size of vessels allowed to fish
OL,13,Ffor octopus within six miles of the
OL,14,FCornish coast will be limited, amid
OL,15,Fconcerns about the impact on other
OL,16,Ffishing stock.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781277116
OL,3,CEmergency ban on large boats fishing
OL,4,Cfor octopus close to the Cornish coast
OL,6,FThe Cornwall Inshore Fisheries &
OL,7,FConservation Authority (IFCA) met on
OL,8,FFriday 12 June and approved the
OL,9,Fproposal - meaning that affected
OL,10,Fvessels will have to move their pots
OL,11,Fby 1 July.
OL,13,FWho is affected?
OL,15,FMulti-hull vessels more than 10 metres
OL,16,Flong and mono-hull vessels more than
OL,17,F12 metres long will be prohibited from
OL,18,Fusing pots to fish for octopus within
OL,19,Fthe Cornwall IFCA district.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781277116
OL,3,CEmergency ban on large boats fishing
OL,4,Cfor octopus close to the Cornish coast
OL,6,FThe ban will be in place for a whole
OL,7,Fyear, but will be continually
OL,8,Freviewed. Emergency bylaws can be
OL,9,Fsubject to six-month extensions.
OL,11,FSupporters of the ban say it will help
OL,12,Fsmaller boats make a living, with
OL,13,Flarger fishing operators forced to
OL,14,Fmove beyond the bylaw zone.
OL,16,FWhy the rush?
OL,18,FThe purpose of the ban is to manage
OL,19,Fthe impact of octopus potting on
OL,20,Fcrustacean - crab and lobster - stocks
OL,21,Fon the Cornish coast.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781277116
OL,3,CEmergency ban on large boats fishing
OL,4,Cfor octopus close to the Cornish coast
OL,6,FThis comes as a recent dramatic
OL,7,Fpopulation bloom of the common octopus
OL,8,F- Octopus vulgaris - off the South
OL,9,FWest coast has seriously impacted
OL,10,Ffisheries and marine ecosystems.
OL,12,FEarlier this year, researchers from
OL,13,Facross Plymouth put together a report
OL,14,Fwith data from scientists and
OL,15,Ffishermen which showed that catch
OL,16,Frates for brown crabs, lobsters and
OL,17,Fscallops dropped by 30% to 50% in 2025.
OL,19,FThis is because octopus are strict
OL,20,Fcarnivores that rely on this type of
OL,21,Fmarine life for their diet.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781277116
OL,3,CEmergency ban on large boats fishing
OL,4,Cfor octopus close to the Cornish coast
OL,6,FOnly four major population blooms have
OL,7,Fbeen recorded in the past 125 years
OL,8,Fand, according to the research, the
OL,9,Fcurrent bloom appears to be at least
OL,10,Fas extensive as any previously
OL,11,Frecorded.
OL,13,FResearchers surveyed 40 fishers and
OL,14,Ffound that although some had adapted
OL,15,Fto catching octopus and benefitted
OL,16,Feconomically for a period of time,
OL,17,Fover half reported negative impacts
OL,18,Ffrom the population bloom.
OL,20,FWhat happened at the meeting?
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781277116
OL,3,CEmergency ban on large boats fishing
OL,4,Cfor octopus close to the Cornish coast
OL,6,FAhead of the bylaw meeting, the
OL,7,FCornwall IFCA sought feedback from the
OL,8,Ffishing industry and received almost
OL,9,F100 survey responses.
OL,11,FSome of the fishers who responded had
OL,12,Fcaught shellfish their whole lives but
OL,13,Fare being forced to adapt to dwindling
OL,14,Fsupplies.
OL,16,FAround 75% of the vessels in the
OL,17,Ffishing district are smaller than 10
OL,18,Fmetres, so will not be affected.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781277116
OL,3,CEmergency ban on large boats fishing
OL,4,Cfor octopus close to the Cornish coast
OL,6,FThe IFCA said there has been an influx
OL,7,Fof larger vessels heading into Cornish
OL,8,Fwaters to fish for octopus in recent
OL,9,Ftimes.
OL,11,FIt was suggested that these vessels
OL,12,Fshould still be able to fish for
OL,13,Foctopus beyond the bylaw zone - with
OL,14,Freports of octopus available to catch
OL,15,F30 to 40 miles offshore.
OL,17,FThe bylaw was approved, nine votes to
OL,18,Ffive, but will still need to be signed
OL,19,Foff by DEFRA.
OL,21,FWhat is the reaction?
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781277116
OL,3,CEmergency ban on large boats fishing
OL,4,Cfor octopus close to the Cornish coast
OL,6,FSome fishers attending the meeting
OL,7,Fopposed the plans, raising concerns
OL,8,Fover the amount of data provided and
OL,9,Ffears the ban won't have the desired
OL,10,Feffect.
OL,12,FBut speaking after the meeting took
OL,13,Fplace, Andrew Pascoe from Newlyn told
OL,14,FITV West Country he was pleased by the
OL,15,Fdecision.
OL,17,F"I think it's the right way to go, to
OL,18,Ftake that precautionary approach," he
OL,19,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781277116
OL,3,CEmergency ban on large boats fishing
OL,4,Cfor octopus close to the Cornish coast
OL,6,FThe fisherman continued: "Without that
OL,7,Fimmediate regulation being brought in,
OL,8,Fwe could see an influx of thousands
OL,9,Fand thousands of pots, which would be
OL,10,Fdetrimental to the shellfish stocks.
OL,11,FAnd the environmental impact it will
OL,12,Fhave as well."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781277116
OL,3,CEmergency ban on large boats fishing
OL,4,Cfor octopus close to the Cornish coast
OL,6,FHe said: "I'm here to represent the
OL,7,Findustry and what's best for them on
OL,8,Fthe future of the industry, inshore
OL,9,Fand offshore. The offshore boats - the
OL,10,Fmajority have said that they're happy,
OL,11,Fthey've had a really good season
OL,12,Foffshore, they've done well, they've
OL,13,F'had their slice of the cake' in their
OL,14,Fwords. And it's time for the inshore
OL,15,Fvessels to have their slice of the
OL,16,Fcake."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781277116
OL,3,CEmergency ban on large boats fishing
OL,4,Cfor octopus close to the Cornish coast
OL,6,FSam Davis from Cornwall IFCA and
OL,7,FConservation Authority said: "The
OL,8,Fsupport and the input that we had on
OL,9,Fboth sides of the argument from
OL,10,Fworking fisherman and fishing
OL,11,Fbusinesses - it's so important to take
OL,12,Fthose views into consideration."
OL,14,FShe explained: "Larger vessels can
OL,15,Fwork longer strings of pots and they
OL,16,Fcan work throughout the year so they
OL,17,Fare able to be more flexible in terms
OL,18,Fof the weather conditions they can
OL,19,Ffish in."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781277116
OL,3,CEmergency ban on large boats fishing
OL,4,Cfor octopus close to the Cornish coast
OL,6,FShe concluded: "It's thinking about
OL,7,Fthe future of all fishing stocks but
OL,8,Fspecifically in this case about crabs
OL,9,Fand lobsters. But moving forwards, we
OL,10,Fneed to look at the wider environment
OL,11,Fin and around, and how we can look at
OL,12,Fother management measures to protect
OL,13,Fthese valuable stocks that support so
OL,14,Fmany businesses in Cornwall."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
